                            <comment id="68612" author="rhenwood" created="Tue, 8 Oct 2013 17:57:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After discussion, the proposed solution is to provide automatic line wrapping. The next steps are to review this advice: &lt;/p&gt;


